THE MOST VALUABLE RECORD IN EXISTENCE
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The address 'Phillips'Sound Recording Services at 38 Kensington,
    Liverpool L7' isn't going to ring many bells and it certainly
    doesn't figure in the annals of popular music but it really should
    have its place because it was in this small and unsophisticated
    studio 60 years ago on 12th July 1958 that the Quarrymen a.k.a the
    Beatles made their first record.

